# Enforce Type-Safe and Best-Practice TypeScript Code

Generate/modify TypeScript to be strictly type-safe (`no any`), compile cleanly (`npm run precommit:typecheck`), and follow best practices: strict mode, linting (`npm run precommit:lint`), JSDoc for exported functions/complex logic, unit tests for critical code, and schema validation (Zod) for external data.